Rose McGrath was dismissed from St Joseph Middle School in Battle Creek, Michigan, for not meeting academic and attendance standards . 
  The 7th-grader is in remission but still recovering from acute lymphoblastic leukemia treatments . 
  She has missed several days of school because of the recovery process . 
  Her mother says she has been offered a spot back at the school but will attend a public school for now . 
  The school says Rose 'hampered her academic performance' Rose was diagnosed with leukemia in 2012 and has been battling the disease since . 
 